Package: indi-altaircam-dbg
Priority: extra
Section: debug
Architecture: any
Depends: indi-altaircam (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: INDI Driver for Altair Astro cameras
 Driver for Altair Astro cameras.
 .
 This driver is compatible with any INDI client such as KStars or Xephem.
 This package contains the debug symbols for the this driver, useful to investigate problems in INDI.
